data.description: 2-Story Stunner in the Heart of Temecula! This beautiful 4-Bedroom home features soaring vaulted ceilings & oversized windows throughout w/ lots of natural light. Formal living room. Family room w/ brick fireplace. Dining area w/ ceiling fan. Kitchen w/ upgraded cabinets & quartz countertops. Spacious Master Bedroom Suite w/ upgraded bathroom. Huge backyard w/ covered patio & grassy area - perfect for entertaining! Fully gated lot. 3 car garage w/ plenty of driveway parking. Laundry room w/ storage. Solar system. Central AC + heat. Just blocks away from James Day Middle School, Long Canyon Creek Park, & the best shopping, dining, & entertainment the area has to offer!
